divs: Sighting DetailsFour seperate occassions observing objects in sky stationary then moving and changing colors,sited over ocean. One other occassion whereby object was sited just above tree level at first I thought it was a star but was to low I ran to the house to get my wife she to observed it I observed it thrue my binoculars, I went back to the house then came back and it was gone.
Summary: Object sited, changing colors stationary then moving.
